<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Filter and Zend_Filter_Input use TRUE, FALSE, and NULL instead of true, false, and null.  It appears that the de facto standard in all other classes is lowercase for these.</p>

